          <div class="faq-three">
            <!-- faq question -->
            <h1 class="faq-page">How does the webiste works ?</h1>

            <!-- faq answer -->
            <div class="faq-body">
              <p>
                First, you'll have to log in using the assigned username and
                password. After that, you can access the data-entry page. In
                this page, you'll be given a word and you have to identify the
                root/stem of the word using the backspace key on your keyboard.
                Here you'll find three buttons : submit, skip and garbage.
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <b>Submit:</b> After you find the root, using backspace, press enter.
                    The indentified root will be recorded on our database.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <b>Skip:</b> If you are not sure about
                    the root of a word, skip that word by pressing the skip button.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <b>Grabage: </b> If you think the given word is not a valid word, press the
                    garbage button.
                  </li>
                </ul>
                 Please make sure to log out before you exit the
                website.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

